<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>Bilgi 5 harflidir. 5 te 4'ü İlgidir ;D - Sunucu Yönetimi</title><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.dev/" rel="alternate"></link><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.dev/feeds/sunucu-yonetimi.atom.xml" rel="self"></link><id>https://yuceltoluyag.dev/</id><updated>2025-04-11T15:45:00+03:00</updated><subtitle>Linux, Python ve Web Geliştirme Rehberleri</subtitle><entry><title>YunoHost Kurulumu Sırasında Karşılaşılan APT Kilitlenme Hatası ve Çözümü</title><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.dev/yunohost-kurulumu-apt-kilitlenme-hatasi-cozumu/" rel="alternate"></link><published>2025-04-11T15:45:00+03:00</published><updated>2025-04-11T15:45:00+03:00</updated><author><name>yuceltoluyag</name></author><id>tag:yuceltoluyag.dev,2025-04-11:/yunohost-kurulumu-apt-kilitlenme-hatasi-cozumu/</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Debian sunucusunda YunoHost kurulumu sırasında karşılaşılan "APT kilitlenme" hatasını adım adım nasıl çözeceğinizi öğrenin.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;h2 id="giris"&gt;🚀 Giri&amp;scedil;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Debian tabanl&amp;inodot; bir sunucuya &lt;a href="https://yunohost.org"&gt;YunoHost&lt;/a&gt; kurmaya &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot;rken "&lt;code&gt;Could not get lock /var/lib/dpkg/lock-frontend&lt;/code&gt;" hatas&amp;inodot;yla kar&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot;la&amp;scedil;abilirsiniz. Bu hata, genellikle sistemde &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;an ba&amp;scedil;ka bir &lt;code&gt;apt&lt;/code&gt; i&amp;scedil;lemi nedeniyle olu&amp;scedil;ur ve kurulumu kesintiye u&amp;gbreve;rat&amp;inodot;r.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bu makalede, bu hatan&amp;inodot;n neden olu&amp;scedil;tu&amp;gbreve;unu, nas&amp;inodot;l tespit edilece&amp;gbreve;ini ve g&amp;uuml;venli bir &amp;scedil;ekilde nas&amp;inodot;l &amp;ccedil;&amp;ouml;z&amp;uuml;lebilece&amp;gbreve;ini ad&amp;inodot;m ad&amp;inodot;m anlataca&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;z. ✅&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="_1"&gt;&lt;img alt="yunohost-hata-cozumu" src="/images/yunohost-hata-cozumu.webp"/&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id="hatanin-anlami"&gt;🧠 Hatan&amp;inodot;n Anlam&amp;inodot;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hata mesaj&amp;inodot; genellikle &amp;scedil;u &amp;scedil;ekilde g&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;n&amp;uuml;r:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;E:&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Could&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;not&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;get&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;lock&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;/var/lib/dpkg/lock-frontend.&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;It&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;is&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;held&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;by&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;process&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;1241&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;apt&lt;span class="o"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bu, sistemde &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;an ba&amp;scedil;ka bir &lt;code&gt;apt&lt;/code&gt; i&amp;scedil;leminin &lt;code&gt;dpkg&lt;/code&gt; sistemini kilitledi&amp;gbreve;i ve sizin i&amp;scedil;leminizin bu y&amp;uuml;zden engellendi&amp;gbreve;i anlam&amp;inodot;na gelir.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;h2 id="adim-adim-cozum"&gt;🔍 Ad&amp;inodot;m Ad&amp;inodot;m &amp;Ccedil;&amp;ouml;z&amp;uuml;m&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="1-aktif-apt-islemlerini-kontrol-edin"&gt;1. Aktif &lt;code&gt;apt&lt;/code&gt; i&amp;scedil;lemlerini kontrol edin:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;ps&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;aux&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;grep&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;apt
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bu komut, &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;an veya donmu&amp;scedil; &lt;code&gt;apt&lt;/code&gt; s&amp;uuml;re&amp;ccedil;lerini listeler. &amp;Ouml;rne&amp;gbreve;in:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;root&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;1241&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;.3&lt;span class="w"&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;apt&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;upgrade&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-y
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id="2-gerekiyorsa-bu-islemleri-sonlandirin"&gt;2. Gerekiyorsa bu i&amp;scedil;lemleri sonland&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot;n ⚠️&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;kill&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-9&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;1241&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;1240&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;1239&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id="3-kilit-dosyalarini-temizleyin"&gt;3. Kilit dosyalar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; temizleyin 🧹&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;rm&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;/var/lib/dpkg/lock-frontend
sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;rm&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;/var/lib/apt/lists/lock
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id="4-dpkg-yapilandirmasini-duzeltin"&gt;4. &lt;code&gt;dpkg&lt;/code&gt; yap&amp;inodot;land&amp;inodot;rmas&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; d&amp;uuml;zeltin 🛠️&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;dpkg&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;--configure&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-a
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id="5-paket-listelerini-guncelleyin-ve-eksikleri-tamamlayin"&gt;5. Paket listelerini g&amp;uuml;ncelleyin ve eksikleri tamamlay&amp;inodot;n 📦&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;apt&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;update
sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;apt&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;--fix-broken&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;install
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id="6-gerekli-paketi-yukleyin-ornek-libtext-iconv-perl"&gt;6. Gerekli paketi y&amp;uuml;kleyin (&amp;ouml;rnek: &lt;code&gt;libtext-iconv-perl&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;apt&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;install&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;libtext-iconv-perl
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id="7-yunohost-kurulumuna-tekrar-baslayin"&gt;7. YunoHost kurulumuna tekrar ba&amp;scedil;lay&amp;inodot;n 🌐&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;curl&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;https://install.yunohost.org&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;bash
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;h2 id="sonuc_1"&gt;✅ Sonu&amp;ccedil;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bu rehberde, YunoHost kurulum s&amp;uuml;recinde s&amp;inodot;k&amp;ccedil;a kar&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot;la&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot;lan &lt;code&gt;dpkg lock&lt;/code&gt; hatas&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; nas&amp;inodot;l &amp;ccedil;&amp;ouml;zece&amp;gbreve;inizi &amp;ouml;&amp;gbreve;rendiniz. Bu y&amp;ouml;ntem yaln&amp;inodot;zca YunoHost de&amp;gbreve;il, genel olarak t&amp;uuml;m &lt;code&gt;apt&lt;/code&gt; tabanl&amp;inodot; kurulumlarda i&amp;scedil;e yarar.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;🔒 Kilitlenmi&amp;scedil; sistemler moral bozabilir ama bu ad&amp;inodot;mlarla h&amp;inodot;zl&amp;inodot;ca &amp;ccedil;&amp;ouml;zebilirsiniz!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;h2 id="ekstra-ipuclari"&gt;📚 Ekstra &amp;Idot;pu&amp;ccedil;lar&amp;inodot;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;E&amp;gbreve;er &lt;code&gt;apt&lt;/code&gt; i&amp;scedil;lemleri s&amp;inodot;k s&amp;inodot;k donuyorsa, sunucunun disk alan&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; kontrol edin.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;htop&lt;/code&gt; komutu ile sistemde genel kaynak kullan&amp;inodot;m&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; takip edebilirsiniz.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uzun kurulum i&amp;scedil;lemlerinde SSH oturumunun kopmamas&amp;inodot; i&amp;ccedil;in &lt;code&gt;tmux&lt;/code&gt; veya &lt;code&gt;screen&lt;/code&gt; kullanabilirsiniz.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yorumlar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z&amp;inodot; a&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;ya b&amp;inodot;rak&amp;inodot;n 💬, ba&amp;scedil;ka bir rehberde g&amp;ouml;r&amp;uuml;&amp;scedil;mek &amp;uuml;zere! 👋&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="Sunucu Yönetimi"></category><category term="yunohost"></category><category term="ssh"></category><category term="debian"></category><category term="apt"></category><category term="linux"></category></entry></feed>